#  Description: local include file 4xx_AWS_LCL
#               Apache and IBM HTTP Server
#  Software products and versions: Apache and IBM HTTP Server
#  Supported OS platforms: AIX, Linux
#  Owner: Marcin Nowakowski
#  Approval information: <reference>
#  
#  Version control
#  1.0 - Marcin Nowakowski / Aurimas Nogis, 2016-05-09
